<item>
            <title>[SPARK-15715] Altering partition storage information doesn&apos;t work in Hive</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-15715</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In HiveClientImpl&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; def toHivePartition(
      p: CatalogTablePartition,
      ht: HiveTable): HivePartition = {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; HivePartition(ht, p.spec.asJava, p.storage.locationUri.map { l =&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Path(l) }.orNull)
  }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Other than the location, we don&apos;t even store any of the storage information in the metastore: output format, input format, serde, serde props. The result is that doing something like the following doesn&apos;t actually do anything:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;ALTER TABLE boxes PARTITION (width=3)
    SET SERDE &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;com.sparkbricks.serde.ColumnarSerDe&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
    WITH SERDEPROPERTIES (&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;compress&apos;&lt;/span&gt;=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
